snippet.title: Friday the 13th: Return to Camp Blood (1998) Fista Productions
snippet.description:
Friday the 13th: Return To Camp Blood {Created: 1998. Release date: 1999, size: 1.11 MB}

Official page:
https://5kids2feed.itch.io/friday-the-13th-return-to-camp-blood

NES demake:
https://8bitslasher.itch.io/f13demake

Ahh, good memories. One of the first games I ever made. Play as Jason & kill the campers. Arrow keys & space bar to play. Crappy graphics I made in mspaint and ripped sounds. I had a shit load of fun making it. Just the idea of making my own video game was amazing to me.
